<br>
Also, as already said, with guildwar broken at the moment a number of interguild battles have been postponed or worked around.  But I think if you lurk around various RP guild boards and the appropriate channels you'll see there's as much going on as ever, if not more. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
